{"tid":979008,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"打過伊拉克戰爭 民主黨37歲女議員宣佈參加總統大選","createTime":"2019-01-12T11:03:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-12T13:03:12.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"645f6251d9de59591b3d76e06ce90a184453d083","tid":979008,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T11:03:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190112/large/1547267479_ddbe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190112%2Flarge%2F1547267479_ddbe.jpg&h=cd582299&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n加伯德宣佈參選總統。(路透社)<br />\n<br />\n美國2020年總統選舉，民主黨到底由誰來挑戰特朗普是黨內重大議題。民主黨37歲女議員加伯德（Tulsi Gabbard）宣佈她將參加總統大選，率先明確表態，如果當選，她不單止會是美國史上首位女總統，更會是最年輕的總統。<br />\n夏威夷民主黨眾議員加伯德於接受美國有線新聞網絡（CNN）訪問時表示：「我已決定參選，將會在下周內發表正式聲明。」她補充指︰「有很多原因促使我參選。美國人民面對很多挑戰，我對此很關心，希望幫助解決問題。」<br />\n現為眾議院外交事務委員會（House Foreign Affairs Committee）成員的加伯德身份特殊，她是首位出生於美屬薩摩亞（American Samoa）的國會議員及首位印度教議員，同時也是一位退役軍人，於2005年派駐伊拉克參加過戰事。<br />\n她另一個惹人爭議的事件，是她於2016年曾與當時準備就任總統的共和黨特朗普會面，亦曾於2017年到訪爆發戰事的敍利亞，私下會晤敍利亞總統巴沙爾（Bashar al-Assad）。就着與巴沙爾會面一事，加伯德曾回應指並非刻意安排，只是「機會來臨」，「我認為應準備好去見任何人，如果有機會可以令戰爭停止。」<br />\n民主黨內躍另外，美國前總統奧巴馬的房屋部長卡斯特羅(Julian Castro)，也表示周六會宣佈參選。另外，女參議院沃倫(Elizabeth Warren)已成立探索委員會，研究是否參選。前副總統拜登也有意思加入戰圈。<br />\n美聯社／法新社／中央社  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190112/59133710\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190112%2F59133710&d=DLtGKLuzkPsemgmfAMyggfM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=6e397f8d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190112%2F59133710&h=a00f548a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190112/59133710</a>"},{"pid":"9d28fcf6f0e56b5a07456d9a28331be8635c62c8","tid":979008,"uid":55043,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T11:08:22.000Z","msg":"又玩咩第一位乜乜第一位乜乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17beb18ff5489a293121f5085b5f51c47aa4f3f6","tid":979008,"uid":42283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T11:10:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鬼佬幾鍾意依type"},{"pid":"db5d457e1f9ab385b6ef52eba3895fd1685596f3","tid":979008,"uid":2429,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"9d28fcf6f0e56b5a07456d9a28331be8635c62c8","tid":979008,"uid":55043,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T11:08:22.000Z","msg":"又玩咩第一位乜乜第一位乜乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T11:21:39.000Z","msg":"政治正確，女權黑人非基督教派<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de9dd793ef48d587df85ebc4c6405b3dae678f8d","tid":979008,"uid":22736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T11:32:12.000Z","msg":"三十七<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 五十七吓嘩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb5ceded1f8ad0c7fa2eaee8b4ddde07637255ea","tid":979008,"uid":121146,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T11:35:15.000Z","msg":"其實係咪史上第一位就一定要選你？<br />\n民主黨肯醒未啊屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d160d885fe36b2ff212ea17f55c84882976fdf68","tid":979008,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T11:51:00.000Z","msg":"亦曾於2017年到訪爆發戰事的敍利亞，私下會晤敍利亞總統巴沙爾（Bashar al-Assad）。就着與巴沙爾會面一事，加伯德曾回應指並非刻意安排，只是「機會來臨」，「我認為應準備好去見任何人，如果有機會可以令戰爭停止。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下一次私下會見習總<br />\n然後話「我認為應準備好去見任何人，如果有機會可以令戰爭停止。」"},{"pid":"fc9e53e1f99d26fa26de47aad50e727a16b92969","tid":979008,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T11:56:15.000Z"